[[Image:Troll.jpg|thumb|125px|Troll depiction.]]

Avatar accounts are created by [[coward]]ly little [[fucktard]]s that have no lives, no [[skill]], no talent, and only have an ability to throw shit and cause [[drama]]. The main purpose of these accounts is to be used by [[trolls]] for mockery, [[harassment]], and insults.


== How An Avatar Account Gets Named ==
The name is created by taking the account name, or something very close to it, of the target of the [[troll]]s [[obsession]], er, hatred, and suffixed with "Avatar". So if the target is "[[Drama Llama|DramaLlama]]", then the Avatar channel name would be "[[Drama Llama|DramaLlama]]Avatar".


== Similarities In Avatar Accounts ==
There are several similarities between all the currently known *Avatar accounts to make one believe they were all created by the same [[troll]].

* All contain the following text in the description box: 'Video Responses Are Automatically Approved'
* Account is always the first to post a comment to it's video with "1st comment"
* All are created in the same style:
** Static background pictures. Usually a still frame captured from the target's own videos
** Static face image lip synced to the voice
** Computer generated TTS voice
* Target account is the only one they are subscribed too.


